al/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35e355aea934eaeb2b131c429ae0fd6f00f831c","tid":479583,"uid":90487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:41:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>失業左成個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打係邊做</blockquote><br />\n係Cobram 做 <br />\n你儲落好多錢咩？ 可以失成個月業咁勁"},{"pid":"065de5c6f2d72fecf296d8537d27d94c56cf8b3f","tid":479583,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:44:21.000Z","msg":"毒撚第一步點搵工搵住宿"},{"pid":"ead3284cdbb1f0e0de5a6706ce2e44b450e2b4d2","tid":479583,"uid":126027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:45:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>失業左成個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打係邊做</blockquote><br />\n係Cobram 做 <br />\n你儲落好多錢咩？ 可以失成個月業咁勁</blockquote><br />\n我都係VIC個邊 錢既話普通啦 夠用咁<br />\n我都諗緊要唔要去採cherry好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6add4e924ae5ed58bafd5e3824e407f2231e48","tid":479583,"uid":17865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T11:45:41.000Z","msg":"留個名 出埋bonus出發"},{"pid":"767aeffe228a73a66f8cd28cd35e114d6d15a486","tid":479583,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T12:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>囡唔洗問啦 通常都係撈果瓣架啦</blockquote><br />\n邊瓣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n🖕🤑✊👄🎉👍"},{"pid":"991927cfdaa980bf2367c5d88c499e896d6531ef","tid":479583,"uid":90487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T17:50:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚第一步點搵工搵住宿</blockquote><br />\n我係一到步住幾日motel個啲先 去gumtree 同啲台灣網站搵工<br />\n搵到工再去返工個到住 返工個啲多數有提供住宿<br />\n睇你想唔想住佢個到 唔想就要自己搵<br />\n問清楚佢有冇綁住宿 如果佢綁死住宿又冇工返就係咁食你租錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90efda4b97360590ca1a9de62a356eba7fbd3beb","tid":479583,"uid":90487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T17:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>失業左成個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打係邊做</blockquote><br />\n係Cobram 做 <br />\n你儲落好多錢咩？ 可以失成個月業咁勁</blockquote><br />\n我都係VIC個邊 錢既話普通啦 夠用咁<br />\n我都諗緊要唔要去採cherry好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有冇採過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果新手唔係搵好多 好似我咁勉強夠食夠交租"},{"pid":"bfd1c61c833bb5b4278c669a1e8a382a02e25ec1","tid":479583,"uid":90487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T17:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留個名 出埋bonus出發</blockquote><br />\n諗住黎一年定兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d694ac20d802efb298986689429eede58680925d","tid":479583,"uid":112649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T18:58:37.000Z","msg":"下年出發lm"},{"pid":"e693b1d02a9318ac98a10eb95e759ac13ee0623a","tid":479583,"uid":60858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T19:31:28.000Z","msg":"嗰時去wh我第一站揀咗墨爾本，好幸運地未夠一個月就喺city搵到份16蚊嘅工，老細同同事都好好，又因為我年紀大唔係為賺錢而去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以一直做到離開墨記為止。<br />\n<br />\n做生果同工廠真係好辛苦，希望大家唔好畀人拖糧，返工平平安安！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6c48861a15f45d7b41ea55c08e93efa3c3f052f","tid":479583,"uid":2933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T00:46:23.000Z","msg":"留個名下年去"},{"pid":"b02e1e8834590a0c4e67717142be056426f2eaa0","tid":479583,"uid":152533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:14:02.000Z","msg":"有無阿德做過雞廠既同志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n阿德雞廠 我返晏就同晚上<br />\n26蚊個鐘，一星期五天工作<br />\n星期六日返工double pay<br />\n好懷念之前澳洲生活<br />\n返左黎香港半年好辛苦"},{"pid":"bf15378b8424e47e948d52ba670dc529902fa7d2","tid":479583,"uid":126027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:29:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>失業左成個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打係邊做</blockquote><br />\n係Cobram 做 <br />\n你儲落好多錢咩？ 可以失成個月業咁勁</blockquote><br />\n我都係VIC個邊 錢既話普通啦 夠用咁<br />\n我都諗緊要唔要去採cherry好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有冇採過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果新手唔係搵好多 好似我咁勉強夠食夠交租</blockquote><br />\n冇採過 夠食夠交租 好過我依加咁冇收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 有冇人有興趣12月去塔斯集二簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4483789752cc22a1b5d652636cfeb4b8643b4982","tid":479583,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:33:41.000Z","msg":"14年果陣去完返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家慢慢同班台狗鬥做爛市啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16128b38f9a613658c6bd389382db605010dbbe","tid":479583,"uid":126027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:50:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>14年果陣去完返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家慢慢同班台狗鬥做爛市啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人工冇22.86唔做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8e473887e09df020915219fa9052a2a98d60dce","tid":479583,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:31:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>14年果陣去完返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家慢慢同班台狗鬥做爛市啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢個岩....佢地個邊22K,換到22K都會心足...仲成日會講唔好做爛市,要尊重專業之類...真係...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b90060266a7eadf17641b9cee5e4ec564edacb","tid":479583,"uid":90487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T07:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嗰時去wh我第一站揀咗墨爾本，好幸運地未夠一個月就喺city搵到份16蚊嘅工，老細同同事都好好，又因為我年紀大唔係為賺錢而去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以一直做到離開墨記為止。<br />\n<br />\n做生果同工廠真係好辛苦，希望大家唔好畀人拖糧，返工平平安安！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拖糧就冇試過 但有遇到個西工頭 香港西女人黎<br />\n本身係上一個地方做緊識咗個香港人 佢地做咗一陣就走咗  佢地去識嘅香港工頭到做 六個鐘車程遠嘅地方<br />\n過咗一兩個星期 佢地就撩我地去佢地到做 應承咗搵好屋俾我地住  點知過到去佢地仲未搵到屋要我地住工頭屋企先 不過其實咁個問題都唔算大 個問題係個西女人嫌我地人多 日日對住我地西口西面 屋又係你地未搵到 我地住佢屋企又有俾租 唔明佢西乜鳩<br />\n終於見識到平時係facebook會見到個啲香港西呀嬋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f265c87c2adf50b2b48c6280299fb11a00a09bd9","tid":479583,"uid":90487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T07:21:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>14年果陣去完返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家慢慢同班台狗鬥做爛市啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人工冇22.86唔做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最底工資"},{"pid":"81828b199484733bb5ec1e4a83b7f03700378c3d","tid":479583,"uid":53901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T00:43:40.000Z","msg":"有無人e+係syd打緊工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}